title.narrative: HIV/AIDS Prevention, Care and Support for Key Populations, PLHIV and General Population

description.narrative: Liberia - HIV - Population Services International - PSI HQ. This program has the following goals: To stop new HIV infections in Liberia. To turn around the tuberclosis epidemic in Liberia. Keep PLHIV alive and healthy in Liberia. To mitigate socio-economic impact on people infected and affected by HIV and AIDS in Liberia. The objectives of this program are: To increase access to HIV prevention and treatment services. To provide HIV prevention information and services to key and vulnerable populations. To increase care and support for PLHIV. Strengthen national health and community systems. . . . . .
